room_title: Escape room "Escape from the Grande Strand Hotel" by Riddles Escape Room in Myrtle Beach
room_address: 9713 N. Kings Highway Myrtle Beach, SC 29577
room_description: Welcome to the Grande Strand Hotel! It has every service that one could hope for, private terraces and the most luxurious accommodations. There is only one problem: all guests check in, but most never leave. It's like they vanish into the darkness of the long hotel halls. Where are they? Will you unravel the mystery, or become one of the missing?
